Dreda Say Mitchell: 'I'm black and voting for Leave. That shocks people'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Novelist, broadcaster and journalist Dreda Say Mitchell explains the thinking behind her position on the EU referendum, and why some people are alarmed by it.

